    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“MUBOSAMA” 是一款以都市传说为题材的冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294750/extras/2e7634a3ad7692628653820208342417.avif?t=1761521569\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ 故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个闷热的日子里，我们度过了平常的夏天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抓甲虫、追狗、找到好地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后，我们得知了她的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那位无脸的神……MUBOSAMA。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一直以来……她都在我们身边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294750/extras/06d0a369f847a48f56aa15e9e9e65cc0.avif?t=1761521569\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ 游戏特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    走动时会触发各种事件的步行模拟器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    调查物品以推进故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    没有任务标记或时间限制，能够轻松游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    她想和所有人一起玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多结局：6</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长：30-60分钟 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ 视频直播指南</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    无论个人或公司，均可无需许可进行直播。</p>",
